title: United Kingdom Imports of Organic Chemicals
description: Imports of Organic Chemicals in the United Kingdom decreased to 664.29 GBP Million in September from 1063.63 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Organic Chemicals in the United Kingdom averaged 664.96 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1170.79 GBP Million in April of 2022 and a record low of 351.42 GBP Million in December of 2003. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Organic Chemicals.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
